1 Be it enacted by the People of the State of Maine as follows:
2 Sec. 1. 30-A MRSA §4364-A, sub-§1, as amended by PL 2023, c. 192, §6, is
3 further amended to read:
4 1. Use allowed. Notwithstanding any provision of law to the contrary, except as
